d/9557037\">9557037</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Ned+Tijdschr+Geneeskd&amp;rft.atitle=%5BThe+Montignac+method%3A+scientific+foundation+debatable%5D&amp;rft.volume=142&amp;rft.issue=5&amp;rft.pages=238-42&amp;rft.date=1998-01&amp;rft_id=info%3Apmid%2F9557037&amp;rft.aulast=van+der+Pant&amp;rft.aufirst=KA&amp;rft.au=Holleman%2C+F&amp;rft.au=Hoekstra%2C+JB&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMontignac+diet\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span><span class=\"citation-comment\" style=\"display:none; color:#33aa33; margin-left:0.3em\">CS1 maint: Unrecognized language (<a href=\"/wiki/Category:CS1_maint:_Unrecognized_language\" title=\"Category:CS1 maint: Unrecognized language\">link</a>) </span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://care.diabetesjournals.org/content/20/3/241.full.pdf+html?ijkey=d98cf8009902b7f21980d0babe2d2bd89b5619f6&amp;keytype2=tf_ipsecsha\">Ann M. Coulston, MS, RD Gerald M. Reaven MD; Stanford University Medical Center - Editorial in <i>Diabetes Care</i> Much Ado about (Almost) Nothing</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Dumesnil01-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Dumesnil01_5-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation journal\">Dumesnil, Jean G.; Turgeon, Jacques; Tremblay, Angelo; Poirier, Paul; Gilbert, Marcel; Gagnon, Louise; St-Pierra, Sylvie; Garneau, Caroline; Lemieux, Isabelle; Pascot, Agn\u00e9s; Bergeron, Jean; Deap\u00e9s, Jean-Pierre (2001). \"Effect of a low-glycaemic index\u2013low-fat\u2013high protein diet on the atherogenic metabolic risk profile of abdominally obese men\". <i>British Journal of Nutrition</i>. <b>86</b> (05): 557. <a href=\"/wiki/Digital_object_identifier\" title=\"Digital object identifier\">doi</a>:<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//doi.org/10.1079/BJN2001427\">10.1079/BJN2001427</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=British+Journal+of+Nutrition&amp;rft.atitle=Effect+of+a+low-glycaemic+index%E2%80%93low-fat%E2%80%93high+protein+diet+on+the+atherogenic+metabolic+risk+profile+of+abdominally+obese+men&amp;rft.volume=86&amp;rft.issue=05&amp;rft.pages=557&amp;rft.date=2001&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1079%2FBJN2001427&amp;rft.aulast=Dumesnil&amp;rft.aufirst=Jean+G.&amp;rft.au=Turgeon%2C+Jacques&amp;rft.au=Tremblay%2C+Angelo&amp;rft.au=Poirier%2C+Paul&amp;rft.au=Gilbert%2C+Marcel&amp;rft.au=Gagnon%2C+Louise&amp;rft.au=St-Pierra%2C+Sylvie&amp;rft.au=Garneau%2C+Caroline&amp;rft.au=Lemieux%2C+Isabelle&amp;rft.au=Pascot%2C+Agn%C3%A9s&amp;rft.au=Bergeron%2C+Jean&amp;rft.au=Deap%C3%A9s%2C+Jean-Pierre&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMontignac+diet\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span> See however a comment to this paper: <cite class=\"citation journal\">Wolever, Thomas M. S. (2007). \"Low carbohydrate does not mean low glycaemic index!\". <i>British Journal of Nutrition</i>. <b>88</b> (02): 211. <a href=\"/wiki/Digital_object_identifier\" title=\"Digital object identifier\">doi</a>:<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//doi.org/10.1079/BJN2002603\">10.1079/BJN2002603</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=British+Journal+of+Nutrition&amp;rft.atitle=Low+carbohydrate+does+not+mean+low+glycaemic+index%21&amp;rft.volume=88&amp;rft.issue=02&amp;rft.pages=211&amp;rft.date=2007&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1079%2FBJN2002603&amp;rft.aulast=Wolever&amp;rft.aufirst=Thomas+M.+S.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AMontignac+diet\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"displ